 plating, resistant to damage, covers her head and feet, along with tusks made of the same material. The underside of her trunk is scaly with spikes, and she has small eyes on the sides of her head. Gammoth is occasionally seen with legs encased in snow clumps.\\n\\nGammoth breathes snow to encase enemies and create icy armor for its legs. It uses its trunk to create a vortex, drawing in hunters to trample them. Primarily relying on brute strength and size, Gammoth deals with threats effectively.\\n\\nElement: Ice Element\\nAilment: Iceblight\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Thunder Element\\nLength: 455 cm to 2617 cm / Height: Large\\nFanged Beast\\n\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":27,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":27,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":29,\"keys\":[\"Elderfrost\",\"Elderfrost Gammoth\",\"World's Greatest Peak\",\"Silver Ridge\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Elderfrost Gammoth\",\"content\":\"Elderfrost Gammoth (Also called: \\\"Elderfrost\\\", \\\"World's Greatest Peak\\\", \\\"Silver Ridge\\\") features bluish fur, silvery-white back fur, and larger tusks compared to regular Gammoth. The bony plate on her scalp is asymmetrical with a large crack, presenting distinct differences.\\n\\nElderfrost Gammoth differs from the regular version by coating its legs and trunk with ice instead of snow. Additionally, it hurls larger snowballs compared to a regular Gammoth.\\n\\nElement: Ice Element\\nAilment: Iceblight\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Thunder Element\\nLength: 455 cm to 2617 cm / Height: Large\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":28,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":28,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":30,\"keys\":[\"Blango\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Blango\",\"content\":\"White-furred ape-like creature with a bright red face, resembling a mix of a Mandrill and a Japanese macaque. The skin beneath its coat is a dull purple color.\\n\\nBlango, a creature that can burrow under snow or stalk rock and ice, often hunts in packs. While individually weak, they become ferocious when led by a Blangonga.\\n\\nLength: ~370 cm / Height: Small\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\