r_notes\":false}},{\"id\":33,\"keys\":[\"Conga\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Conga\",\"content\":\"They resemble pink gorillas with a face of a hippopotamus, black underbellies and have a blonde patch of hair on top of their head.\\n\\nThey are known for their ability to charge at hunters, like Bullfangos (but slower), travel in packs, and fart on hunters.\\n\\nHeight: Small\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":32,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":32,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":34,\"keys\":[\"Congalala\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Congalala\",\"content\":\"The Congalala resembles a giant, tailed gorilla with pink fur, a hippo-like head, and long front claws. Its head spike signifies pack leadership, and despite its appearance, Congalalas are surprisingly intelligent beasts.\\n\\n\\nDespite their seemingly adorable appearance, Congalalas should not be underestimated. Mostly docile, they react strongly to the presence of herbivores and can become aggressive when disrupted or startled. In rage mode, their upper jaw and backside turn red, releasing fart gas, and their aggression significantly increases.\\n\\nElement: Fire Element (Specific Food Eaten)\\nAilment: Fireblight, Sleep, Soiled, Poison, Paralysis, Blastblight\\nWeakness: Fire Element\\nLength: 491 cm - 1670 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":33,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":33,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":35,\"keys\":[\"Congalala\",\"Emerald Congalala\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Emerald Congalala\",\"content\":\"The Emerald Congalala, distinguished by its green and white coloration, features a larger beard and taller hair spike compared to the normal Congalala. It produces greater amounts of gas and farts more frequently.\\n\\nThe Emerald Congalala, when consuming objects held by its tail, can exhale dangerous stomach fluids. Eating a mushroom results in breath causing Poison, Sleep, Paralysis, or flames, while consuming other items leads to effects similar to its farts.\\n\\nElement: Fire Element (Specific Food Eaten)\\nAilment: Fireblight, Sleep, Soiled, Poison, Paralysis, Blastblight\\nWeakness: Ice Element\\nLength: 491 cm - 1670 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":34,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":34,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":36,\"keys\":[\"Rajang\",\"Golden Mane\",\"Gold Lion\",\"Destruction Incarnate\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Rajang\",\"content\":\"Rajang (Also called:  \\\"Gold Lion\\\", \\\"Destruction Incarnate\\\", \\\"Golden Mane\\\") closely resembles the Blangonga, sharing ape-like features and some attacks. However, Rajang stands out with broader muscles, large horns, a hairy tail tip, and the ability to use electricity-based attacks. Brown in color, with crimson eyes and gold horns, Rajang's fur turns gold when enraged.\\n\\nRajang is an extremely violent and ultra-aggressive creature, fiercely territorial and known to pick fights with anything entering its domain, including Elder Dragons. In combat, it relies on extreme physical strength and agility, overwhelming enemies with sheer power and unrelenting aggression. It can shoot electricity from its mouth and enters a heightened \\\"Rampage Mode\\\" for increased speed and power, with toughened forelimbs that deflect most attacks. This mode can be interrupted by damaging or severing its tail or after a set duration.\\n\\nElement: Thunder\\nAilment: Thunderblight\\nWeakness: Ice Element\\nLength: 729 cm - 1632 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":35,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":35,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":37,\"keys\":[\"Gold Lion\",\"Super Simian\",\"Furious Rajang\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Furious Rajang\",\"content\":\"Furious Rajang (Also called \\\"Gold Lion\\\", \\\"Super Simian\\\") is an exceptionally powerful variant that has lost its tail, either naturally or by self-removal, enabling it to fully unleash its abilities. In Rage mode, its fur stands up, and it is surrounded by an electric aura, showcasing its heightened power.\\n\\nFurious Rajang is an exceptionally aggressive monster with rage surpassing even its notorious normal variant. Its normal state mirrors a regular Rajang's Rage Mode, exhibiting increased strength, speed, and aggression. It introduces new thunder attacks, including shooting electric balls in the air and a ground slam with electric shockwaves. Unlike regular Rajang, hitting the tail does not affect Furious Rajang's rampage mode; instead, it must be struck in the head.\\n\\nElement: Thunder\\nAilment: Thunderblight\\nWeakness: Ice Element\\nLength: 869 cm - 1188 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":36,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":36,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":38,\"keys\":[\"Bloodlust Incarnate\",\"Blue Bear Beast\",\"Arzuros\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Arzuros\",\"content\":\"Arzuros is recognized for its turquoise fur and ursine body, featuring a ridge of erect hair along its nose and a tough hide on its back. The claws have elongated red nails with protective braces around the wrists. Arzuros has large legs, small feet, and a short, wide tail.\\n\\nArzuros wields two vicious claws for its primary attacks, utilizing its large body and surprising agility for charging attacks and pinning down prey.\\n\\nArzuros, omnivorous creatures, enjoy feasting on fish and honey. While consuming honey, they become oblivious to their surroundings. When threatened by larger monsters, Arzuros attempts to intimidate with size and claws or uses agility to escape. They often hang their tongues out of their mouths.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: None\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Ice Element\\nSize: 501 cm - 854 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\\n\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":37,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":37,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":39,\"keys\":[\"Redhelm\",\"Redhelm Arzuros\"],\"secondary_keys\":[\"Apex Arzuros\",\"Fanged Beast\",\"Medium Monster\",\"Arzuros\"],\"comment\":\"Redhelm Arzuros\",\"content\":\"Redhelm Arzuros, among the largest of their species, exhibit distinctive features such as blood-red forearms, feet, eyes, and upper body-fur. The rest of their bodies are primarily blue, with a greenish-blue carapace and lower body-fur. A pronounced strip of fur atop their head gives the impression of a mohawk.\\n\\nRedhelm Arzuros leverage their increased size and strength in battles, showcasing impressive abilities. They leap high into the air, aiming to crush opponents upon landing with incredible force. Utilizing larger claws and powerful arms, they rip through the ground, hurling debris. In watery environments, they can even send entire schools of fish flying using this technique.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: Stun\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Ice Element\\nSize: 781 cm - 904 cm / Height: Medium\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":38,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":38,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":40,\"keys\":[\"Apex Arzuros\"],\"secondary_keys\":[\"Snowbaron Arzuros\",\"Fanged Beast\",\"Medium Monster\",\"Arzuros\"],\"comment\":\"Apex Arzuros\",\"content\":\"Apex Arzuros has a dark coloration with red scars and eyes, showcasing large forelimbs like Redhelm Deviants. When enraged, its red scars glow.\\n\\nAggressive Apex Arzuros attacks with massive forelimbs, calls for monster assistance during a Rampage, and can destroy defenses in one hit. In rage, it performs powerful moves like a ground slam and rock throw. It also steals and eats honey from hunters like its normal counterpart.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: Stun\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Ice Element, Thunder Element\\nSize: 781 cm - 904 cm\\nFanged Beast\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":39,\"useProbability\":tru