rue,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":56,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":56,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":58,\"keys\":[\"Supremacy Wyvern\",\"Infernal Black God\",\"Akantor\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Akantor\",\"content\":\"Akantor (Also called: \\\"Supremacy Wyvern\\\", \\\"Infernal Black God\\\") is a massive, turtle-like wyvern with reddish-black spikes, durable shells, large claws, and formidable tusks. Despite being classified as a Flying Wyvern, it has lost the ability to fly.\\n\\nAkantors, immensely powerful and feared, disrupt ecosystems with their presence. They instigate fear among creatures, with only the most formidable daring to challenge them. Armed with incredible strength, imposing spines, giant tusks, and corrosive saliva, Akantors are formidable adversaries. Their roars, capable of creating a potent sonic beam with the Dragon Element, add to their deadly arsenal.\\n\\nAkantors are relentless predators, dominating ecosystems with their strength. They attack anything in sight, making them a formidable force only rivaled by elder dragons or skilled hunter teams.\\n\\nElement: Fire Element, Dragon Element\\nAilment: Defense Down, Fireblight, Dragonblight\\nWeakness: Dragon Element, Thunder Element\\nLength: 3049 cm / Height: Large\\nFlying Wyvern\\n\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":57,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":57,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":59,\"keys\":[\"The Tyrant of Ice\",\"Avalanche Wyvern\",\"The White God\",\"Ukanlos\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Ukanlos\",\"content\":\"Ukanlos (Also Called: \\\"The Tyrant of Ice\\\", \\\"The White God\\\", \\\"Avalanche Wyvern\\\") resembles Akantor, with a silvery-white carapace, jagged fins, and a compact face. Despite being classified as a Flying Wyvern, it can't fly as its wings have disappeared.\\n\\nUkanlos uses its massive, serrated shovel-like chin to fling ice and dig through frozen surfaces. It can swim underground, cutting through ice and causing projectiles. It unleashes a powerful ice beam from its mouth, crushes foes with its weight, and can leap great distances by slamming its tail on the ground.\\n\\nElement: Ice Element\\nAilment: Iceblight\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Thunder Element\\nLength: 3188 cm / Height: Large\\nFlying Wyvern\\n\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":58,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":58,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":60,\"keys\":[\"Tigrex\",\"Absolute Power\",\"Roaring Wyvern\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Tigrex\",\"content\":\"Tigrex (Also Called: \\\"Roaring Wyvern\\\", \\\"Absolute Power\\\") is a formidable quadrupedal wyvern with a massive head, powerful limbs, and distinctive yellow/blue striped coloration. Its head features horn-like ears, and its segmented tail ends in a spiny protrusion.\\n\\nTigrex is a fast quadrupedal wyvern with wings adapted into forelegs. While it rarely flies traditionally, it can glide. Tigrex boasts powerful lungs for loud, concussive roars, causing physical damage. Unlike some monsters, Tigrex lacks elemental attacks, relying on sheer strength and its deafening roar in battles.\\n\\nTigrex uses a loud roar to intimidate, and in intense combat, it enhances its appearance with a bright-red glow to intimidate further.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: None\\nWeakness: Thunder Element, Dragon Element\\nLength: 1388 cm - 2914 cm / Height: Medium\\nFlying Wyvern\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\"