lying Wyverns are large, bipedal monsters with wings. Renowned for their flight mastery, most have evolved powerful wings, while some are quadrupedal, using wings as forearms. Others in this class can be flightless or wingless. Notably diverse, some winged species may have limited flight capabilities.\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":105,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":105,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":107,\"keys\":[\"Strange Bird\",\"Yian Kut-Ku\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Yian Kut-Ku\",\"content\":\"The Yian Kut-Ku (Also called: \\\"Strange Bird\\\") is a wyvern recognized by its distinct fan-like ear frills, large yellow beak with a central pink stripe, and orange-pink plating. With deep blue wing membranes, bright yellow eyes, and a small, agile build, it boasts powerful hearing thanks to its frills circling the ears.\\n\\nThe Yian Kut-Ku, known for its speed due to a light build, can launch flaming projectiles from its flame sac. In moments of rage, it releases three projectiles while moving faster. It exhibits a temperamental, skittish, and inquisitive nature, often attempting to seem larger by spreading