roam the coral landscape in large flocks, occasionally feeding on coral eggs. The flock can be cleverly led to certain places if a hunter grabs hook on one, as the rest will follow where that individual will go.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: none\\nWeakness: none\\nLength: ~ 425 cm / Height: Small\\nWingdrake\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":225,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":225,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":227,\"keys\":[\"Noios\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Noios\",\"content\":\"Noios are wingdrakes that resemble vultures in addition to pterosaurs. They have a large beak, a waddle hanging from their neck, light-brown skin, and a long tail.\\n\\nNoios are flying creatures in the Wastes that emit a startling cry and can mimic the roar of Diablos when threatened. Luring them to the ground with raw meat allows hunters to defeat and carve them for materials.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: none\\nWeakness: none\\nLength: ~ 525 cm / Height: Small\\nWingdrake\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"we