keys\":[\"Great Dracophage Bug\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Great Dracophage Bug\",\"content\":\"Large Dracophage Bugs ale like Great Thunderbugs but Dragon Element energy is said to lie dormant within their bodies. These glimmering creatures still hold many secrets yet to be discovered.\\n\\nElement: Dragon Element\\nAilment: Paralysis\\nWeakness: Water Element\\nLength: ~ 80 cm / Height: Tiny\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":244,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":244,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":246,\"keys\":[\"Piercing Beetle\",\"Seltas\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Seltas\",\"content\":\"Seltas (also called: \\\"Piercing Beetle\\\") is a large insectoid with a colorful exoskeleton, six legs, weaponized forelegs, collapsible wings, and a head with compound eyes and slicing mandibles. It is the male counterpart to the Seltas Queen.\\n\\nSeltas is agile in the air, using well-developed wings for precise movement. Its forelimbs are equipped for jabbing and slashing, and it can spear prey with its armored canopy. Additionally, it can shoot three green globs causing the Defense down ailment.\\n\\nSeltas is a powerful airborne predator with weaponized forelimbs. When forced to merge with the Seltas Queen, he becomes a loyal companion, under her complete control.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: Defense Down, Fatique\\nWeakness: Thunder Element, Fire Element\\nLength: 541 - 769 cm / Height: Medium\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":245,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":245,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":247,\"keys\":[\"Axe Beetle\",\"Seltas\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Desert Seltas\",\"content\":\"The Desert Seltas (also called: \\\"Axe Beetle\\\") features a green, orange and brown shell, and seems to have reduced flight capacity. Its canopy features a double-pronged structure, rather than the single barbed spine of the common species, and its eyes shine a bright green. \\n\\nUnlike the common species, Desert Seltas is capable of digging through the sand to attack prey from below. It can also shoot three yellow globs that cause paralysis.\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: Paralysis\\nWeakness: Thunder Element, Ice Element\\nLength: 541 - 766 cm / Height: Medium\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":246,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":246,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":248,\"keys\":[\"Heavy Beetle\",\"Seltas Queen\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Seltas Queen\",\"content\":\"The Seltas Queen (also called: \\\"Heavy Beetle\\\") is a large, beetle-like Neopteron that resembles a scorpion and posesses no wings with a lustrous green exoskeleton, beige stripes, orange spines, six limbs four of which make contact with the ground, the other two being used for digging and grasping prey, and a long, segmented tail with a large pincer.\\n\\nSeltas Queen uses her large limbs and weaponized tail, employing the Water element with rapid-fire water globs. She can cast pheromones to attract Seltas and inflict stench on hunters. The duo performs combined attacks, with Seltas on top of Seltas Queen, including unique maneuvers like Seltas lifting and throwing the Queen during charges.\\n\\nSeltas Queen relies on Seltas for transportation and protection but can exhibit extreme violence, including killing and devouring him for energy.\\n\\nElement: Water\\nAilment: Waterblight, Soiled, Stun\\nWeakness: Fire Element, Ice Element\\nLength: 1271 - 1791 cm / Height: Large\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":247,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":247,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":249,\"keys\":[\"Cannon Beetle\",\"Desert Seltas Queen\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Desert Seltas Queen\",\"content\":\"Desert Seltas Queen (Also called: \\\"Cannon Beetle\\\") has a brownish olive-green shell and a narrower tail pincer than that of the common species. Her eyes are bright green like those of the Desert Seltas. \\n\\nThe tail seems much longer and more articulate and is able to pull her digging male counterpart out of the sand. She is even capable of using her tail to mount and launch a mate or a pinned hunter on a water blast with startling accuracy, the former shattering the drone to pieces and enabling pulling a new drone out of the ground.\\n\\nElement: Water\\nAilment: Waterblight, Soiled, Stun\\nWeakness: Water Element, Ice Element, Thunder Element\\nLength: 1760 cm - 2291 cm / Height: Large\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"ext