false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":251,\"keys\":[\"Ahtal-Ka\",\"Pavilion Mantis\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Ahtal-Ka\",\"content\":\"Ahtal-Ka (Also called: \\\"Pavilion Mantis\\\") is a large insectoid monster with a golden body resembling a devil's flower mantis. It has six limbs, including four walking legs and two raptorial legs with wing-like extensions. The headpiece resembles a Pharaoh's crown, and it has purple eyes with tiny black pupils, giving it an insectoid sphinx appearance.\\n\\nAhtal-Ka compensates for its lack of physical strength by using golden silk to bind steel beams to its back, throwing them at enemies. It is dangerous even without them, attacking with sharp claws and releasing a pheromone that reduces hunters' defense.\\n\\nAhtal-Ka uses it's silk to create Ahtal Nesto, (Also called: \\\"Ahtal-Ka's Throne\\\", \\\"Ahtal-Ka's Nest\\\", \\\"Ahtal-Ka's Fortress\\\", \\\"Empress' Throne\\\", \\\"Walking Fortress\\\"\\n\\nElement: None\\nAilment: Defense Down, Webbed\\nWeakness: Water Element, Ice Element, Thunder Element\\nSize: ~ 1504 cm / Height: Large\\nNeopteron\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":250,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":250,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_descripti