werful axe and a shield and sword combo. It boasts a length suitable for both close and mid-range combat. While it has moderate weight, its ability to switch between two modes adds tactical depth, allowing hunters to adapt to different situations during monster encounters. The Charge Blade's unique mechanics involve storing energy in the shield to unleash devastating attacks in axe mode.\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"depth\":4,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"displayIndex\":366,\"useProbability\":true,\"characterFilter\":null,\"excludeRecursion\":false,\"linked\":true,\"embedded\":false,\"position\":1,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":366,\"probability\":100,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":null,\"cooldown\":null,\"delay\":null,\"match_persona_description\":false,\"match_character_description\":false,\"match_character_personality\":false,\"match_character_depth_prompt\":false,\"match_scenario\":false,\"match_creator_notes\":false}},{\"id\":368,\"keys\":[\"LBG\",\"Light Bowgun\"],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"Light Bowgun\",\"content\":\"The Light Bowgun, or \\\"LBG\\\" (~ 70 cm) is a ranged weapon known for its mobility and rapid-fire capabilities. It is relatively compact, allowing hunters to maintain agility during combat. Despite its lightweight design, the Light Bowgun can fire a variety of ammunition types, providing versatility in dealing with different monsters. Its ability to support various elemental shots and status effects makes it a strategic choice for hunters who prefer ranged combat.\",\"constant\":false,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"en